node.title: Searching for Gretchen Anthony: The evidence
node.description: Investigators searching for a missing Florida mother soon realized someone was using the COVID-19 pandemic to cover up her disappearance.
node.content: ["Investigators searching for a missing Florida mother soon realized someone was using the COVID-19 pandemic to cover up her disappearance.", "During the early months of the\u00a0 pandemic, friends and family received texts from the phone of a beloved Florida mother, Gretchen Anthony. The texts said she had an \"acute\" case of coronavirus. When no one could reach her by phone, friends and family \u2013 who believed it wasn't Gretchen sending those texts -- called the police for help.\u00a0", "Here is a closer look at the case.\u00a0"]
